# Import Status

[Back to All Imports](/tenant-admin/imports)

| Property | Value |
|----------|-------|
| Status | <%= @import.status %> |
<% if @import.started_at -%>
| Started | <%= @import.started_at.strftime("%Y-%m-%d %H:%M:%S") %> |
<% end -%>
<% if @import.completed_at -%>
| Completed | <%= @import.completed_at.strftime("%Y-%m-%d %H:%M:%S") %> |
<% end -%>
| Imported By | <%= @import.user.name %> (`<%= @import.user.email %>`) |

<% if @import.error_message.present? -%>
## Error

<%= @import.error_message %>

<% end -%>
<% if @import.record_counts.present? && @import.record_counts.any? -%>
## Imported Records

<% @import.record_counts.each do |type, count| -%>
- **<%= type.humanize %>:** <%= count %>
<% end %>
<% end -%>
<% if @import.user_mapping.present? && @import.user_mapping.any? -%>
## User Mapping

| Email | Status |
|-------|--------|
<% @import.user_mapping.each do |email, mapping| -%>
| <%= email %> | <%= mapping["matched"] ? "Matched" : "Placeholder created" %> |
<% end %>
<% end -%>
<% if @import.status == "completed" && @import.collective_id -%>
<% imported_collective = Collective.tenant_scoped_only(@import.tenant_id).find(@import.collective_id) -%>
---

[Go to Imported Collective](/collectives/<%= imported_collective.handle %>)
<% end %>
